title: Buck Owens Live at The Birchmere, Alexandria, VA, May 1st, 1989
description:
Hello!

This concert recording has been floating around for some years now. After some research I have come to the conclusion that this concert was held at The Birchmere May 1st and not March 1st as has always been claimed. The calendar from The Birchmere is included. Also corrected was removal of silence inserted by encoder when encoding to FLAC. This was done manually in Audacity without additional steps. The show now plays without any annoying gaps. Enjoy!!
